Class MoodEvent

java.lang.Object
com.example.team_16.models.MoodEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MoodEvent extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a mood event recorded by a user. This class encapsulates all information related to a single mood event, including the emotional state, timestamp, location, and other details.
